long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Removes the fbclid parameter from URL before navigating to page.
Fbclid stands for Facebook Click Identifier (“Facebook Click Identifier”).
The parameter can be used for analytics and advertising purposes.
